Too immaculate?  Have you people played 10??  Good god, talk about something that looks like it was pulled from a disco dance hall.  They're facing a world plagued by Sin, and yet everything is beautiful and bright colors.  I half expected to see a Lava Lamp somewhere in there, or bean bag chairs.  It looked like the bedroom of this acidhead I used to live with... everything was neon and looked like it woulda glowed in the dark.  That bugged the @#%$ outta me.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
