<br>
This will make the game almost trivially easy until the final dungeons.<br>
<br>
The very first boss you fight, Draw Siren (GF).. you probably have already done this.  Go to GF menu.. make sure Siren is learning -- &quot; L Mag-RF &quot;  Refines life/recovery magic from items.<br>
<br>
Once you get this ability (only costs 30 ap - IE 1 boss or 20 min of fighting), you can refine 10 Curaga (most powerful cure spell) from 1 tent (1000gp).  Now provided you test up to ~ SeeD level 10 or so, within.. 1 hr of walking around leveling/drawing, you should have ~20,000 gp.  Buy 20 tents.  Turn 20 tents into 200 curaga.  Junction 100 curaga to hp on 2 chars.. when you get enough money, do it for your 3rd char.  This gives you +2500 hp or so.. provided you don't level your ass off, you should be able to breeze through the entire game w/o worrying much at all about leveling / drawing etc.<br>
<br>
For those that are frustrated ~~ or lazy.<br>
<br>
I replayed it and its much better the 2nd time, cuz you actually know how to use Junction and can enjoy the story a bit more.<br>
